pytraj.analyses package¶

Submodules¶

pytraj.analyses.Analysis module¶

class pytraj.analyses.Analysis.Analysis¶

Bases: object

The abstract base class that all other actions inherit. By convention actions have 3 main phases: init, Setup, and DoAnalysis. Init is used to initialize the action, make sure that all arguments for the action are correct, and add any DataSets/DataFiles which will be used by the action. Setup will set up the action for a specific Topology file. DoAnalysis will perform the action on a given frame. A fourth function, Print, is for any additional calculations or output the action may require once all frames are processed.
